                            <comment id="72178" author="almalki.a" created="Tue, 1 Nov 2011 10:06:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually a similar issue (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-299&quot; title=&quot;ConcurrentSessionFilter to support removal of remember-me cookies&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SEC-299&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SEC-299&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) was fixed a long time ago, and it provided a setter to inject a list of logout handlers. However, when using namespace config, this behavior is not used and only the default SecurityContextLogoutHandler is used...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
